FBIS4-9621 "dreeu083_k_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-083 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 CROATIA Internal Affairs Ministry Finds Explosives Internal Affairs Ministry Finds Explosives LD2604191394 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1730 GMT 26 Apr 94 LD2604191394 Zagreb HTV Television Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The Croatian Ministry of Internal Affairs has uncovered a certain quantity of highly destructive plastic explosives in the wider area of the city of Zagreb. These explosives belong to the former Yugoslav People's Army and were to have been used for sabotage and terrorist actions in Zagreb and the Republic of Croatia, a statement by the Ministry's Public Relations Department says, among other things.
